<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
  <meta charset="utf-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>Action Required: Payment Failed for Resume Matcher Pro</title>
  <style>
    body {
      font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
      line-height: 1.6;
      color: #333;
      max-width: 600px;
      margin: 0 auto;
      padding: 20px;
    }
    .header {
      background-color: #e74c3c;
      color: white;
      padding: 20px;
      text-align: center;
      border-radius: 5px 5px 0 0;
    }
    .content {
      padding: 20px;
      border: 1px solid #ddd;
      border-top: none;
      border-radius: 0 0 5px 5px;
    }
    .footer {
      margin-top: 20px;
      text-align: center;
      font-size: 12px;
      color: #777;
    }
    .button {
      display: inline-block;
      background-color: #e74c3c;
      color: white;
      padding: 10px 20px;
      text-decoration: none;
      border-radius: 5px;
      margin-top: 15px;
    }
    .alert {
      background-color: #fff8f8;
      border-left: 4px solid #e74c3c;
      padding: 15px;
      margin: 20px 0;
    }
    .details {
      background-color: #f9f9f9;
      padding: 15px;
      border-radius: 5px;
      margin: 20px 0;
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="header">
    <h1>Payment Failed</h1>
  </div>
  <div class="content">
    <p>Hi {{name}},</p>
    
    <div class="alert">
      <p><strong>Action Required:</strong> We weren't able to process your payment for Resume Matcher Pro.</p>
    </div>
    
    <p>We attempted to charge your payment method for <strong>{{currency}}{{amount}}</strong>, but the payment was declined. This could be due to:</p>
    
    <ul>
      <li>Insufficient funds</li>
      <li>Expired card</li>
      <li>Incorrect payment details</li>
      <li>Bank declined the transaction</li>
    </ul>
    
    <div class="details">
      <h3>Payment Details:</h3>
      <p><strong>Amount:</strong> {{currency}}{{amount}}</p>
      <p><strong>Attempt count:</strong> {{attemptCount}}</p>
      <p><strong>Next automatic retry:</strong> {{nextAttemptDate}}</p>
    </div>
    
    <p>To avoid any interruption to your Resume Matcher Pro subscription, please update your payment method as soon as possible. Click the button below to update your billing information:</p>
    
    <p style="text-align: center;">
      <a href="{{paymentLink}}" class="button">Update Payment Method</a>
    </p>
    
    <p>If you need any assistance with your payment or have any questions about your subscription, please don't hesitate to contact our support team by replying to this email.</p>
    
    <p>Best regards,<br>
    The Resume Matcher Team</p>
  </div>
  <div class="footer">
    <p>Â© {{currentYear}} Resume Matcher. All rights reserved.</p>
    <p>
      <a href="{{paymentLink}}">Update Payment</a> |
      <a href="{{appUrl}}/settings/billing">Manage Subscription</a> |
      <a href="{{appUrl}}/settings">Account Settings</a>
    </p>
  </div>
</body>
</html>